## 3. Hard Rules (Non-Negotiable)

- One feature in `in_progress` at a time.
- `./check.sh` must pass before declaring a feature `done`.
- For `sdd: true` features: spec → human approval → implement → review → done.
- Never edit the approved spec.
- Every R<n> must end up with at least one test.

